OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScottish football to ban   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fheading around match days  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Professional footballers in Scotland   
OL,6, are to be banned from heading the ball 
OL,7, in training the day before and the day 
OL,8, after a game.                          
OL,10,FClubs are also being told to limit     
OL,11,Fexercises that involve repetitive      
OL,12,Fheading to one session per week.       
OL,14,FThe new guidelines come after Glasgow  
OL,15,FUniversity research that showed former 
OL,16,Ffootballers were three-and-a-half times
OL,17,Fmore likely to die from brain disease. 
OL,19,FExperts believe there could be a link  
OL,20,Fto repetitive heading of the ball.     
